            <title>[OWB-785] WebContextsService isn&apos;t compatible with actor-frameworks</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OWB-785</link>
                <project id="12310844" key="OWB">OpenWebBeans</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;with the current implementation of WebContextsService it isn&apos;t possible to use actors which resolve e.g. @ApplicationScoped beans, because &apos;applicationContexts&apos; is a ThreadLocal which isn&apos;t initialized if an actor-framework created the thread. it&apos;s needed e.g. if batches in a web-app are based on an actor-framework.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
